  37,123,Yaha! Achiika! (Annabi) Iliyasu daa be Naawuni tuumba ni
  37,124,"Saha shőĶli o ni daa yőĶli o niriba: ‚ÄúDi ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, yi ku zo Naawuni?‚ÄĚ"
  37,125,"‚ÄúDi ni b…ĒŇč…Ē, yi jőĶmdi la ba‚Äôal, 1 ka chőĶri (Duuma so) Ňäun gari sokam nambu?‚ÄĚ"
  37,126,"‚ÄúNaawuni n-ny…õ yi Duuma, ni yi banim ban daa daŇč yi tooni maa gba Duuma.‚ÄĚ"
